{"tid":553950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【休班警又入一球！】葵涌運動場內嘈交 休班女輔警涉打傷12歲女童","createTime":"2018-02-08T04:32:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-08T06:32:05.000Z","uid":102586,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"bdcf87214988ea9029eb28778450a83b6e18d66e","tid":553950,"uid":102586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T04:32:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180203/57790072\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180203%2F57790072&d=G8A4%2Btb3AoGxh5fllcsGhG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=22546971\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180203%2F57790072&h=6a2648f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180203/57790072</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>葵涌運動場內嘈交 休班女輔警涉打傷12歲女童</strong><br />\n<br />\n休班輔警涉傷人被捕。上周日(28日)中午12時許，39歲姓羅休班女輔警於葵涌運動場因瑣事問題爭執，其間涉嫌用手襲擊一名12歲女童。警方接報到場，經初步調查，羅女涉嫌襲擊致造成實際身體傷害被捕。羅女報稱腰痛，而女童則肩部受傷，兩人一併由救護車送往瑪嘉烈醫院治理。案件由葵青警區重案組第一隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n該名姓羅休班女輔警已獲准保釋候查，須於二月下旬向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n死差婆，細路女都唔放過，冇性架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c40d2c2f55fc81e602d832725d3d53b18353bd3b","tid":553950,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T04:39:22.000Z","msg":"識玩 報稱腰痛 姐係歐鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"058057b4606db01eba12e2dbeb5244425e79041a","tid":553950,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T04:42:01.000Z","msg":"goal"},{"pid":"0b455d4655fe403ae08707ea0fe44dde5d07bcd2","tid":553950,"uid":3656,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote"